events.name: ゴブリン討伐　ラスト

parameters:
\n< Serena >...I can't find anything. Was it just my
imagination...?

\n< Serena >Wha...t... A green, infant... A goblin
baby? This is...
$gameScreen.showPicture(60,"Mns-ゴブリン/Mns001-赤子01-素体",0,0,76,100,100,255,0)
Goblin Baby: Agi... Agigi...

\n< Serena >Ugh, uuu... Wha, what...! Just looking
at it... makes my chest feel uneasy...!
$gameScreen.showPicture(60,"Mns-ゴブリン/Mns001-赤子01-素体",0,0,76,100,100,255,0)
Goblin Baby: Gii-...!
\n< Serena >No, no way...!

\n< Serena >Ha... I ended up running away without
thinking...

\n< Serena >Even though it's just a powerless
infant, the mere fact that it resembles
a human makes it feel so repulsive...

\n< Serena >Extermination... is it... okay...? After
all, a single one won't survive for
long.

\n< Serena >Rather, I don't want to go back to the
hut...

\n< Serena >However, if I return without proof of
subjugation again, the Master will scold
me...
\n< Serena >No, I did make an effort. Indeed.
\n< Serena >An effort, indeed.
\n< Guild Master >Yes... yes. I thought as much...

\V[2501]\n< Serena > left. Good, good.  With this, the
matter is settled.
'　ゴブリン討伐は完了だ。宿に帰って休もう。'
'クエストをクリアした。'
回想セーブ 温泉街ゴブリン敗北
Mmm, huh... Hah!?\n< Serena >
Gyii! Gyiii!\n< Goblin >
Eek!?\n< Serena >
W-what is this situation...!?\n< Serena >

(Dragged into a nest...? Pinned down by
goblins... There are roughly seven of
them around...)\n< Serena >

The ring is here... If only I could
generate the Affabilis...\n< Serena >
Gugya!\n< Goblin >
Stop it! Don't pull!!\n< Serena >
Stop, stop--\n< Serena >
Gegya!\n< Goblin >

Aaahhh! My clothes...! Let go! Don't
look!!\n< Serena >

(Damn it... My concentration... is
disrupted...! Because of something like
this... I can't regenerate my
equipment...!)\n< Serena >
Gihehehe...\n< Goblin >
*panting*...?\n< Serena >
!?... What are you rubbing against me?!\n< Serena >
It's disgusting...! No...!\n< Serena >
Gyuhhe... Gihh...\n< Goblin >
Hii...!?\n< Serena >
Ah... uh... ah...!\n< Serena >

What is this... It's not an attack...
What am I being subjected to... What are
the goblins doing...?\n< Serena >
セックス _セレナ-ゴブリンTT01-1
セックス _セレナ-ゴブリンTT01-1
...\n< Goblin >

Stop it... Don't bring "that" any closer
to me... It's something very vile...!\n< Serena >

(It seems like something I shouldn't
see...!)\n< Serena >
Get away! Let go... Stop it... ugh!?\n< Serena >
Noooooo!?\n< Serena >
No! No! Not there...!\n< Serena >

Pushing, pressing against me...! Eh!?
No...!\n< Serena >
Gihi... Gi!\n< Goblin >
!投擲物1
!投擲物1
エネミー HK_ゴブリン01-1
エネミー HK_ゴブリン01-1
エリカ HK_PT01-1
エリカ HK_PT01-1

Oh la la! Goblins! Getting it on in
broad daylight!\n< Erika >
Ah... Erika-sama...!?\n< Serena >
Oh? Who do I find here but Serena!\n< Erika >

Seriously, that was a close shave if I
ever saw one!\n< Erika >

Can't be helped then! Consider this a
favor I'm doing for you!\n< Erika >

Ah-tch, ptooey... Damn goblins are so
damn slimy...!\n< Erika >
Serena, are you alright?\n< Erika >

I'm fine. My apologies, Erika-sama... I
owe you one.\n< Serena >

Be more careful. Even weaklings like
them have the strength to kill a human.\n< Erika >
It's a lesson learned.\n< Serena >

Alright. Shall we head back? ...But not
in that state, obviously.\n< Erika >

I'll go look for some clothes or cloth
you can wrap yourself in.\n< Erika >
My apologies...\n< Serena >
Phew...\n< Serena >
What... was that, I wonder...\n< Serena >
It was scary...\n< Serena >

It was a different kind of fear, not
just pain or the fear of death...\n< Serena >

It feels like it will haunt my dreams. I
doubt I'll be able to forget it for a
while...\n< Serena >
Scene_Recollection.prototype.rngd_exit_scene();
Sounds like you had quite the ordeal.\n< Guild Master >
Indeed... I have no face to show.\n< Serena >

How about it? Had enough of being an
adventurer? It's painful, dangerous, and
to top it off, stinks.\n< Guild Master >
...\n< Serena >
No, it's not a problem.\n< Serena >

Certainly, there was fear. I may have
underestimated things.\n< Serena >

But what I must do lies ahead. If so,
then I shall proceed. There's nothing to
do but continue.\n< Serena >
Tch.\n< Guild Master >

Well... at least the goblins are gone
now. Consider the quest complete.\n< Guild Master >

Here, your reward. Go get some sleep,
eat, and take a bath.\n< Guild Master >
...\n< Serena >

\n< Serena > \V[2501] left... Is this the end of the
matter then.
'　危うい所だったが、なんとか依頼は完了した。'
'　今日はもう帰って休もう…。'
'ゴブリンに負けた'
